questionsAndAnswers.question: What do I need before I get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: To develop any website, we need: - Domain - Hosting - Content However, if you do not have any of the above available, please contact us and we can surely assist in arranging all.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is Domain & hosting included in the package?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, Domain & Hosting are a company's property registered to their name, that is provided by the client but we would love to help you find the best host domain registrar OR do all for you in a custom package Please feel free to contact our support anytime and discuss your requirements in details.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Which technologies do you cover/offer?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: WordPress & WooCommerce Shopify React Native Core Languages (HTML/CSS/JS/JQuery/PHP/ etc.)

questionsAndAnswers.question: I like some websites very much , can you create something similar?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Well, I can answer this question after checking the website. You are highly welcome to share your ideas and thought in the inbox, thank you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you set-up business emails on domain e.g., xyz@domain.com?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we can set-up your business emails for whichever email solution you prefer. This is included with all packages.
